data.description: Very well maintained and spacious townhome with no HOA. Many updates to include windows, deck, kitchen with beautiful quartz countertops, bathrooms (one with a soaking tub), downstairs flooring, washer & dryer, roof & gutters. New driveway. Family room with wood burning fireplace. The kitchen is a chefs delight. In the back you'll find a large wood private deck perfect for entertaining. This neighborhood is in an ideal location off of First Colonial. Close to great schools, the hospital, shopping and dining minutes away. Oceanfront a quick drive. Close access to 264.
